00:33:21.680 --> 00:33:25.090
Because we have this popular
image of the refugee as someone

00:33:25.090 --> 00:33:29.290
who has experienced some form of
trauma that makes it impossible

00:33:29.290 --> 00:33:31.310
for them to stay in their home.

00:33:31.310 --> 00:33:34.930
