00:37:59.870 --> 00:38:02.460
So more abstractly,
I think we can talk

00:38:02.460 --> 00:38:04.890
about narratives being
born across borders.

00:38:04.890 --> 00:38:11.380
So as I think I suggested earlier,
the refugee's testimony really

00:38:11.380 --> 00:38:14.540
about his or her own
experience really forms the core

00:38:14.540 --> 00:38:17.340
