has talked about the culture

00:38:22.110 --> 00:38:26.350
of disbelief with which many
asylum adjudicators approach

00:38:26.350 --> 00:38:27.660
these narratives.

00:38:27.660 --> 00:38:33.040
And one of the reasons is that
there are narrative brokers.

00:38:33.040 --> 00:38:35.900
So you can go in your
home country to someone

00:38:35.900 --> 00:38:39.310
who will tell you a story
that's been shown to work

00:38:39.310 --> 00:38:42.120
in the asylum setting
where you're heading.

00:38:42.120 --> 00:38:45.050
And you can adapt it a
little to make it kind

00:38:45.050 --> 00:38:47.490
