witch doctors on call at home

00:39:15.990 --> 00:39:19.480
to curse the trafficked
women's families if they try

00:39:19.480 --> 00:39:22.960
to escape from their traffickers.

00:39:24.930 --> 00:39:26.230
&gt;&gt; Jason Steinhauer: Interesting.

00:39:26.230 --> 00:39:28.870
Ivan, there was an article

